So `(w, w_1) ∈ p_1.tail` or `(w, w_1) = p_1.head`.
The goal `w_1 ∈ p_1.support` means `w_1` is one of the vertices in `p_1.support`.
`p_1.support` is defined as `p_1.head :: p_1.tail`.
So `w_1 = p_1.head` or `w_1 ∈ p_1.tail`.

